Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:49.23,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\blur2\fad(200,200)}你看 太阳会逐渐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:55.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\blur2\fad(200,200)}将光芒下的黑暗驱除的吧
