Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.62,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在舞台的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.62,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直不断挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.67,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不论是后悔 还是空虚
