Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摄像机前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有什么节目呢
