Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算模仿这只Kirara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把摄像机关了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,录制中止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节目开始制作以来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就只是看着 没发表过任何意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你们表现得太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间叫我们出现在电视前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有教过你们 就什么都不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不否定参加电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我们还有很多不成熟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我想举行演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为打压演艺活动愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才更应该多举办些演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所做的事的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我再好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没看过你跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你在歌唱舞动时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会绽放出最耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说你其他的工作做的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 总让人这样认为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法在工作中集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为审判成为了焦点话题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想这样是不是真的算受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的话感动了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在演唱会上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家承认我真正的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想通过实力进入选拔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是凪沙和智理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智理?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大半夜的也在练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yukirin姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来智理在担心自己不是真的这么受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才和翼小姐对着干 想要开演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都还没有总选举的海报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们去看看那个比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娘娘也超赞成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次总选举的啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代前田敦子的录像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这光芒是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想传递给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的声音就是13代啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我可以就这样化作光芒 继续照耀着大家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs46\fad(520,0)\bord0\pos(635,460)}总选举结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望有一天能像啊酱那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代啊酱是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年的总选举上 我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赢啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确此后不久 她就袭名了大岛优子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和现在的我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从研究生的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么直接地挑战前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感受到优子姐的决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}就拜托你们支持我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 大家要鼓起干劲来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干劲满满
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方 她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那事后 铃子她做了调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,播放我们节目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些演艺活动打压严重的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说像演唱会这样人群聚合的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其禁得很严
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不能开演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视节目的话 通过WOTA的地下网络
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以传递给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『心跳不已 躲避球』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的队伍要接受惩罚游戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有跟彼方分到一组 从这点看就完全没希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放弃也太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做就要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice Catch的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森炭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服 衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 又要上了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森姐的Kirara 明明不是演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却可以发光到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众们好像也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织音nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是发自内心觉得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 输掉的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是惩罚游戏的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题出在了彼方之外的战力上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演唱会也好 其他的事情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是要把认真的心情传递给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯~今天的表情不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举的事情 还不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停电?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑一片…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是AKB0048总负责人 片桐翼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始公布星历48年度新单曲选拔总选举的速报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速报是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前总选举的排名发表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 被选出的成员有10位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此也将从第10位开始公布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十位 第9代 北原里英
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第九位 第77期研究生 园智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理…
